== Guides & Documentation

Key resources to support mentors, podlings, and the Incubator PMC. These guides cover onboarding, mentoring practices, governance, reporting, and lessons learned.

- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Mentor+Quick+Start+Guide[Mentor Quick Start Guide] — fast orientation for new mentors, covering core responsibilities  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Quick+Reference+-+Common+Red+Flags[Common Red Flags] — warning signs of podling or community trouble to watch for  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Best+Practices+for+Mentors[Best Practices for Mentors] — 50 practical scenarios and examples for effective mentoring  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Onboarding[Mentor Onboarding] — step-by-step guide for new mentors entering the Incubator  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Offboarding[Mentor Offboarding] — guidance for mentors stepping back after graduation or retirement  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+PMC+Onboarding[Incubator PMC Onboarding] — orientation for joining the IPMC and its oversight role  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Committer+Onboarding[Podling Committer Onboarding] — what new committers need to know when granted access  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+PPMC+Onboarding[Podling PPMC Onboarding] — explains duties of the Podling Project Management Committee  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Selecting+a+PMC+Chair[Selecting a PMC Chair] — process and considerations for appointing a project chair  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Third-Party+Branding+and++Incubating+Projects[Third-Party Branding & Incubating Projects] — rules for naming, branding, and avoiding confusion  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/TRAINING/ASF+Project+Reporting+Guidance[Project Report Guide] — how podlings report to the IPMC and what to include  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Case+Studies[Incubator Case Studies] — real-world examples of podling successes and challenges  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/How+to+Use+the+ASF+Maturity+Model[How To Use the ASF Maturity Model] — applying the model to assess project readiness  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Path%3A+Governance+in+Practice[Governance in Practice] — practical guidance on ASF values and community decision-making  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentors+Tough+Conversation+Guide[Mentors Tough Conversation Guide] — tips for handling difficult discussions with podlings  
